Package: almond-monitor
Version: 0.9.9.2
Maintainer: Andreas Lindell
Architecture: all
Depends: gunicorn, python3, python3-flask, python3-yaml,python3-simplejson, python3-flask-httpauth, python3-matplotlib, zlib1g-dev, nagios-plugins, ksh, sysstat, libsys-statistics-linux-perl, librdkafka1
Description: A local monitoring system running Nagios plugins and exposing the results through various means (http, api, metrics, kafka data stream)
